C2AUD.original: ~z~That strange feeling deep inside - that's the feeling of satisfaction after you did something good.
C2AUD.translated: ~z~你心中的奇妙感觉，那是做善事后的满足感。

C2AUD.original: C2_AB
~z~Most murders are committed by people you know.
C2AUD.translated: ~z~大部分谋杀案都是熟人犯罪。

C2AUD.original: ~z~I've found his place, there are a bunch of guys hanging around.
C2AUD.translated: ~z~我找到他的位置了，那边聚集了很多人。

C2AUD.original: C2_DA
~z~But most of us don't want to kill them when we find them.
C2AUD.translated: ~z~但大部分人不会在找到他后把他杀了。

C2AUD.original: ~z~He must be in there, Niko. Dispose of them all. We're doing a favor for our comrades in the East.
C2AUD.translated: ~z~他一定在那儿，Niko。歼灭他们。我们是在给东部的同志们帮忙。

C2AUD.original: C2_CA
~z~Congratulations. Goodbye.
~z~You better start doing me some favors soon.
~z~Most wives are killed by their husbands.
C2AUD.translated: ~z~大部分妻子都是被丈夫杀害的。

C2AUD.original: ~z~Yes.
C2_AA
~z~Someone with something to lose, but not much to live for.
C2AUD.translated: ~z~都是不想失去某物，但活着也没啥盼头的人。

C2AUD.original: ~z~Did you serve your purpose?
~z~You know a lot.
C2_CB
C2_CE
~z~So... you fought in the war...
~z~Okay, okay! That's enough man!
~z~I should never have thought I could beat you people.
C2AUD.translated: ~z~我就不该以为自己能打败你们的。

C2AUD.original: ~z~Then you are that much closer to finding the man you are after.
C2AUD.translated: ~z~那你离你找的人又近了一步。

C2AUD.original: ~z~We always use people like you. Karen - Michelle... she was the same.
C2AUD.translated: ~z~我们经常利用你这样的人。比如Karen－Michelle...她也一样。

C2AUD.original: ~z~Yes. You're looking for some people.
~z~Oh, I'm joking... I'm sure she does.
C2AUD.translated: ~z~哦，我说笑的...我相信还是要的。

C2AUD.original: ~z~Two things. One, you don't get a hundred murders pinned on you.
C2AUD.translated: ~z~两点。第一，不会有指向你的上百起谋杀。

C2AUD.original: ~z~At least I am not being sent back to the homeland. I do not wish to think what they would do to me.
C2AUD.translated: ~z~至少我不会被遣送回国。我都不敢想他们会怎么对我。

C2AUD.original: C2_AC
~z~I am sure your wife doesn't need to sleep around.
C2AUD.translated: ~z~我相信你老婆不用和人乱搞，也会...

C2AUD.original: ~z~Alright, you win!
~z~This country is not free, your constitution is all lies!
C2AUD.translated: ~z~这个国家并不自由，你们的宪法满篇谎言！

C2AUD.original: C2_BA
~z~What's in it for me?
C2_CD
C2_CC
~z~Interesting...
~z~This democracy you people speak of is all illusion!
~z~We're all looking for that special someone.
C2AUD.translated: ~z~我们都在寻找那个特别的人。

C2AUD.original: ~z~Come in, Niko.
~z~Funny. I'm divorced. My wife can sleep with whoever she wants.
C2AUD.translated: ~z~真好笑。我离婚了。我老婆想和谁睡就和谁睡。

C2AUD.original: ~z~Be staying away from me!
~z~Now get access to a police computer and wait for my message. Go!
C2AUD.translated: ~z~现在先访问警用电脑，等我发你短信吧。去吧！

C2AUD.original: ~z~I need you to go find someone for me.
~z~The government is all powerful, there is no beating you!
C2AUD.translated: ~z~政府太强大了，根本打不过它！

C2AUD.original: ~z~Two... maybe I will help you. And maybe I won't.
C2AUD.translated: ~z~第二...我或许会帮助你。抑或是不帮。

C2AUD.original: ~z~Yes. And my wife had better stop sleeping with that tennis coach, or...
C2AUD.translated: ~z~没错。所以我老婆最好别再和那个网球教练上床了，不然...

C2AUD.original: C2_DB
~z~I'm not divorced. I was never married. No details.
C2AUD.translated: ~z~别说离婚了。我压根没结过婚。不许深究。

C2AUD.original: ~z~Hi.
~z~So why use me?
~z~I'm joking.
~z~I'll be getting a picture through shortly. This is important.
C2AUD.translated: ~z~待会儿我给你发张图。图很重要。
